quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  49,14,"Anthu okhala m’midzi amati, “Ife timakhulupirira.” Nena, “Inu mulibe chikhulupiriro. Koma nenani kuti, “Tadzipereka kwa Mulungu chifukwa chikhulupiriro sichidakhazikike m’mitima mwanu. Ndipo ngati inu mumvera Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake, Iye sadzachepetsa ntchito zanu, ngakhale m’pang’ono pomwe. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wokhululukira nthawi zonse ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha.”"
  49,15,okhulupirira ndi okhawo amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake ndipo sakayika ngakhale ndi pang’ono pomwe. Iwo amadzipereka kwathunthu pamodzi ndi chuma chawo m’njira ya Mulungu. Ndipo iwo ndiwo olungama
  49,16,"Nena, “Kodi inu mungamuphunzitse Mulungu za chipembedzo chanu? Pamene Mulungu amadziwa chilichonse chili mlengalenga ndi padziko lapansi. Ndipo Mulungundi wodziwa chilichonse"
  49,17,"Iwo amaganiza kuti ali kukuchitira iwe chisoni pamene alowa Chisilamu. Nena, “Inu simuli kundichitira ine chisoni polowa chisilamu. Iyayi, koma ndi Mulungu amene wakuchitirani inu chisoni pokulangizani njira yoyenera ngati inu, muli anthu olungama.”"
  49,18,Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa zobisika zonse zimene zili mlengalenga ndi padziko lapansi ndipo Mulungu amaona zonse zimene mumachita
  50,1,Qaf. Pali Buku lolemekezeka la Korani
  50,2,"Koma iwo alikudabwa kuti kwa iwo kwadza mchenjezi wochokera pakati pawo. Motero anthu osakhulupirira amati, “chimenechi ndi chinthu chachilendo!”"
  50,3,"“Pamene ife tafa ndi kusanduka dothi, kubwerera kotero ndi kosatheka.”"
  50,4,Ife timadziwa onse amene adamezedwa ndi nthaka ndipo Ife tili ndi Buku la mbiri yawo
  50,5,"Iyayi, koma iwo adakana choonadi pamene chidadza kwa iwo. Kotero iwo, tsopano, asokonezeka"
  50,6,Kodi iwo sayang’ana kumwamba ndi kuona mmene tidakukonzera ndi kukukongoletsera ndi kuona kuti kulibe mipata
  50,7,Ndipo dziko lapansi Ife talipanga kukhala losalala ndi kuikamo mapiri ndipo tidameretsa mu dzikolo mbewu zokongola zosiyanasiyana
  50,8,Choonetsa ndi chikumbutso kwa kapolo aliyense amene amatembenukira nthawi zonse kwa Mulungu
  50,9,Ndipo timatumiza kuchokera ku mitambo mvula yodalitsika ndipo timameretsa m’minda mbewu zimene zimakololedwa
  50,10,Ndi mitengo italiitali ya tende yolemedwa ndi zipatso
  50,11,Chakudya cha akapolo. Ndipo Ife timapereka moyo kunthaka imene idali yakufa. Kumeneko ndiko kuuka kwa akufa
  50,12,"Adakana iwo asanadze, anthu a Nowa ndi iwo amene anali kukhala ku Ar-rass ndi Thamoud"
  50,13,Anthu a mtundu wa Aad ndi Farawo ndi abale ake a Loti
  50,14,"Ndi iwo amene anali kukhala m’nkhalango ndi anthu a ku Tuba, aliyense wa iwo adakana Atumwi ndipo chenjezo langa lidakwaniritsidwa"
  50,15,Kodi Ife tidatopa ndi chilengedwe choyamba? Iyayi. Iwo asokonezeka ndi nkhani zokhudza chilengedwe chatsopano
  50,16,Ndithudi Ife tidamulenga munthu ndipo timadziwa zimene mtima wake umamuuza. Ndipo Ife tili pafupi ndi iye kuposa mtsempha wa moyo wake
  50,17,"Pamene asungi awiri amulandira, wina atakhala kudzanja lamanja ndi wina ku dzanja lamanzere"
  50,18,Palibe mawu amene amayankhula amene samveka kwa Msungi wa tcheru
  50,19,Ndipo ululu wa imfa udzadza pa iye mwachoonadi. Ichi ndicho chimene iwe unali kuyesetsa kuchithawa
  50,20,Ndipo lipenga lidzaombedwa ndipo limeneli lidzakhala tsiku loopseza
  50,21,Ndipo mzimu uliwonse udzadza pamodzi ndi mngelo wouyendetsa ndi mngelo wochitira umboni
  50,22,"(Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa anthu ochimwa) kuti, “Ndithudi inu simudafune kuchenjezedwa za chimenechi ndipotsopano Ifetavundukulachimenechimakuphimbani. Ndipo lero maso anu ali kuona zenizeni.”"
  50,23,"Ndipo mnzake adzati, “Uwu ndi umboni umene ndili nawo.”"
  50,24,“Ponyani ku Gahena aliyense wosathokoza ndiponso wosamvera.”
  50,25,"“Woletsa kuchita ntchito zabwino, woswa malamulo ndiponso wokayika.”"
  50,26,"“Iye amene anali kukhazikitsa milungu ina yoonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni, motero mponyeni ku chilango chowawa.”"